  <prompt>Create `scripts/Deploy-RedisCache.ps1` extracting Redis provisioning logic from `Provision-Customer.ps1:422-492`. Parameters: `-Environment {dev|staging|prod}`, `-WhatIf`, `-VerifyOnly`, `-CutoverBffSettings`, `-Force` (required to touch prod/demo per NFR-05). Idempotent (`az deployment group create`); KV secret upsert (`Redis-ConnectionString`); post-deploy verification via `RedisValidationTests.ps1`. Returns non-zero exit on failure.</prompt>
  <role>Spaarke infrastructure developer with PowerShell + Az CLI familiarity. Apply `script-aware` skill (load `scripts/README.md` first).</role>
