  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read `Provision-Customer.ps1:422-492` Redis block. Extract: Bicep deploy invocation, output extraction (redisHostName, connection string), KV secret upsert.</step>
    <step order="2">Read reference pattern `deploy-session-files-index.ps1` for: pre-flight checks, post-deploy invariant verification, exit codes.</step>
