    <step order="4">Author `Deploy-RedisCache.ps1` with `[CmdletBinding(SupportsShouldProcess)]`. Parameters per FR-11. Header doc-comment block (Spaarke conventions).</step>
    <step order="5">Implement env-to-paramfile mapping: dev ŌåÆ `redis-dev.bicepparam`, staging ŌåÆ `redis-staging.bicepparam`, prod ŌåÆ `redis-prod.bicepparam` (with `-Force` gate).</step>
    <step order="6">Implement deploy: `az deployment group create` against the appropriate RG (dev ŌåÆ `spe-infrastructure-westus2` per spec). Capture outputs.</step>
    <step order="7">Implement KV secret upsert: parse outputs; build connection string (host + SSL port + password); `az keyvault secret set` to `Redis-ConnectionString` in target KV. Determine KV via parameter or env mapping.</step>
    <step order="8">Implement `-VerifyOnly`: skip deploy; run `RedisValidationTests.ps1` against existing instance; return non-zero on any failure.</step>
